Game Code: 1.60 CDC Strategy:
Optional: Make sure TOWER is lit (7). Shoot standups (1) until mode lights (2) are blinking. The amount of bank hits might vary depending on setting but default is one bank cleared.
Shoot left ramp (3) to start CDC. Do NOT shoot CDC ramp again. Instead go for 3-4 left loop (4) barn hits. Shoot left ramp (3) at least 5 times.
Optional: If TOWER (6) is lit shoot RIOT (8). If not, then shoot standups (9) to light TOWER (6).
If you skipped TOWER you can shoot either red arrow once then finish the mode shooting CDC (3).
You can add time by completing target bank (1) if needed.
AAM ballsy bloodbath strategy.
Shoot zombies (X) 15 times. Light TOWER via standups (9). Shoot target bank (1) until Blood Bath is lit (B). During multiball make sure your inlane X is never collected until super jackpot is ready. Super jackpot will be ready when any 2/3 of the FOOD, WEAPONS, FIRST AID is collected. Collect the double scoring by shooting RIOT (8) Make sure only one target remain and use left ramp (3) to get a nice feed to the right flipper. Be sure to have inlane X lit and make the last standup fall for a massive super jackpot! My biggest one scored 382M. I believe I had about 18X scoring. 9X inlane + double scoring.

AAM Tunnel + Crossbow strategy! Check video on the left!
Shoot zombies (X) 15 times. Complete the WEAPON bank (W). Start TUNNEL mode (Y). Start CROSSBOW at ARENA ramp (U). Collect the X multiplier in the inlane. Make ANY red ARROW for massive score!
In video I have 11X multiplier which gives me: CROSSBOW: 121M TUNNEL: 55M Plus some change for zombie hit.
